  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive the days of past social gaming networks in <strong>VIDEOVERSE</strong> – A decision-based narrative adventure focusing on character development, friendship and love, from the developer behind <i>One Night Stand</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Emmett, a young video game fan and aspiring artist, dive into this fictional video game era, where the <i>Kinmoku Shark</i> gaming system and its online social network, <i>Videoverse</i>, were still popular. Strengthen Emmett’s friendships, share fan art and browse the lively gaming communities. Make decisions that will change how Emmett grows, his approach to Videoverse and, ultimately, the final outcome!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will your actions help Videoverse thrive, or will you get caught up in teenage drama, video game fandoms and corporate conspiracies?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/4591554b3260501eeffa2344d496e324.poster.avif?t=1774367444\" aria-label=\"Animated VIDEOVERSE drawing GIF. Many pixel illustrations from the game scroll by. \" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/4591554b3260501eeffa2344d496e324.webm?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/4591554b3260501eeffa2344d496e324.mp4?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relive the Days of Retro Gaming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VIDEOVERSE is inspired by Miiverse, MSN messenger, early internet forums and 00’s technology. The chill soundscape of the Kinmoku Shark, composed by Clark Aboud (<i>Slay the Spire, Kind Words</i>), will uncover memories of your favourite retro gaming consoles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/135c25baf9536dcbf0f01f899e67064f.poster.avif?t=1774367444\" aria-label=\"Animated VIDEOVERSE community GIF. Scrolling down various posts in the Feudal Fantasy Community.\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/135c25baf9536dcbf0f01f899e67064f.webm?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/135c25baf9536dcbf0f01f899e67064f.mp4?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Browse Videoverse</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet a huge cast of characters, unlock multiple side stories, enjoy the pixel doodles, and seek out the truth behind the troubled social gaming network! Personalise your Videoverse experience by choosing your avatar, personal quote and favourite theme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/de4d789cde485c44294706cc80e3c813.poster.avif?t=1774367444\" aria-label=\"Animated Feudal Fantasy GIF. Hanzo runs to Umi and embraces her. Then, they look up at a burning castle.\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/de4d789cde485c44294706cc80e3c813.webm?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/de4d789cde485c44294706cc80e3c813.mp4?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join Feudal Fantasy Fans</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accompany Emmett as he plays the Kinmoku Shark’s most popular JRPG, Feudal Fantasy. Swap theories and discover tips from other FF fans in its exclusive Videoverse community…and find out whether or not Hanzo will be able to stop the evil Nobunaga!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>VIDEOVERSE contains several accessibility options:</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear Font</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Closed Captions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colourblind Friendly Themes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Content Warnings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound, Music and Voice Volumes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tip Button</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive the days of past social gaming networks in <strong>VIDEOVERSE</strong> – A decision-based narrative adventure focusing on character development, friendship and love, from the developer behind <i>One Night Stand</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Emmett, a young video game fan and aspiring artist, dive into this fictional video game era, where the <i>Kinmoku Shark</i> gaming system and its online social network, <i>Videoverse</i>, were still popular. Strengthen Emmett’s friendships, share fan art and browse the lively gaming communities. Make decisions that will change how Emmett grows, his approach to Videoverse and, ultimately, the final outcome!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will your actions help Videoverse thrive, or will you get caught up in teenage drama, video game fandoms and corporate conspiracies?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/4591554b3260501eeffa2344d496e324.poster.avif?t=1774367444\" aria-label=\"Animated VIDEOVERSE drawing GIF. Many pixel illustrations from the game scroll by. \" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/4591554b3260501eeffa2344d496e324.webm?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/4591554b3260501eeffa2344d496e324.mp4?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Relive the Days of Retro Gaming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VIDEOVERSE is inspired by Miiverse, MSN messenger, early internet forums and 00’s technology. The chill soundscape of the Kinmoku Shark, composed by Clark Aboud (<i>Slay the Spire, Kind Words</i>), will uncover memories of your favourite retro gaming consoles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/135c25baf9536dcbf0f01f899e67064f.poster.avif?t=1774367444\" aria-label=\"Animated VIDEOVERSE community GIF. Scrolling down various posts in the Feudal Fantasy Community.\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/135c25baf9536dcbf0f01f899e67064f.webm?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/135c25baf9536dcbf0f01f899e67064f.mp4?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Browse Videoverse</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet a huge cast of characters, unlock multiple side stories, enjoy the pixel doodles, and seek out the truth behind the troubled social gaming network! Personalise your Videoverse experience by choosing your avatar, personal quote and favourite theme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/de4d789cde485c44294706cc80e3c813.poster.avif?t=1774367444\" aria-label=\"Animated Feudal Fantasy GIF. Hanzo runs to Umi and embraces her. Then, they look up at a burning castle.\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/de4d789cde485c44294706cc80e3c813.webm?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2079180/extras/de4d789cde485c44294706cc80e3c813.mp4?t=1774367444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join Feudal Fantasy Fans</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accompany Emmett as he plays the Kinmoku Shark’s most popular JRPG, Feudal Fantasy. Swap theories and discover tips from other FF fans in its exclusive Videoverse community…and find out whether or not Hanzo will be able to stop the evil Nobunaga!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>VIDEOVERSE contains several accessibility options:</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clear Font</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Closed Captions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colourblind Friendly Themes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Content Warnings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound, Music and Voice Volumes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tip Button</p></li></ul>",
